&lt;p&gt;Pilgrims Hospices is seeking applicants for a domestic assistant vacancy at our hospice in Thanet. As member of the Domestic team, post holders will be responsible for undertaking cleaning duties for all hospice facilities under the direction of the Domestic Supervisor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must be available for early starts and weekend working as well as occasional evening work as required. Experience working in a similar role is desirable but not essential as training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contracted hours are 20 per week and will be worked on a rota basis.&lt;/p&gt;
